---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout
  title="Access & Licensing - ByteLite LLC"
  description="Early Supporter access and ByteLite enterprise compression licensing. ByteLite LLC."
>

  <section class="pricing-section">
    <div class="container">
      <h2>Access &amp; Licensing</h2>
      <p class="section-intro">
        Support the ecosystem or license the infrastructure.
      </p>

      <div class="pricing-grid">

        <!-- Early Supporter -->
        <div class="pricing-card card-supporter">
          <div class="card-stage stage-supporter">Early Supporter</div>
          <div class="plan-header">
            <h3>Early Supporter</h3>
            <div class="price">
              <span class="amount-label">Pay what feels right</span>
            </div>
            <div class="annual-price">$25 minimum. No maximum.</div>
          </div>
          <ul class="features">
            <li>Priority updates on all ByteLite LLC products</li>
            <li>First access to ByteLite demos when available</li>
            <li>HeartStrings App closed beta access (when live)</li>
            <li>Recognition on the project supporter list</li>
            <li>No recurring charges. No obligations.</li>
          </ul>
          <a href="/contact" class="btn btn-supporter">Become a Supporter</a>
        </div>

        <!-- Professional Enterprise -->
        <div class="pricing-card card-enterprise">
          <div class="card-stage stage-enterprise">Professional Enterprise</div>
          <div class="plan-header">
            <h3>ByteLite compression licensing</h3>
            <div class="price">
              <span class="amount">50%</span>
              <span class="period">of savings</span>
            </div>
            <div class="annual-price">No savings = No cost</div>
          </div>
          <ul class="features">
            <li>Bit Motion Encoding compression infrastructure</li>
            <li>Self-reporting API integration (planned)</li>
            <li>Assigned enterprise auditor (planned)</li>
            <li>Annual checksum verification (planned)</li>
            <li>Direct line support</li>
            <li>Custom integration</li>
          </ul>
          <a href="/contact" class="btn btn-enterprise">Contact for Details</a>
        </div>

      </div>

      <!-- Enterprise Model Details -->
      <div class="enterprise-details">
        <h3>ByteLite Enterprise Model</h3>
        <p class="enterprise-note">Enterprise features are under development. Contact us to discuss early access and custom integration requirements.</p>
        <div class="detail-grid">
          <div class="detail-card">
            <h4>Fair Usage Model</h4>
            <p>
              Pay only 50% of your realized cost savings. With ByteLite compression,
              your savings scale with usage. Example: Save $100 in storage/transmission -- pay $50 in licensing.
            </p>
          </div>
          <div class="detail-card">
            <h4>Security and Compliance (Planned)</h4>
            <p>
              Enterprise solutions will integrate self-reporting to the ByteLite LLC API for transparency.
              Annual checksum verification will ensure reporting software integrity.
            </p>
          </div>
          <div class="detail-card">
            <h4>Dedicated Support</h4>
            <p>
              Enterprise clients will receive an assigned Enterprise Solution Auditor for reporting verification,
              application updates, and ongoing optimization consultation.
            </p>
          </div>
          <div class="detail-card">
            <h4>Patent Protection</h4>
            <p>
              ByteLite compression is protected under USPTO patent-pending status.
              Enterprise partnerships are direct licensing agreements with ByteLite LLC.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="trust-note">
        <h4>Trust &amp; Innovation</h4>
        <p>Your licensing fees directly support ByteLite LLC product development and infrastructure research.</p>
      </div>

    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>

<style>
  .pricing-section {
    padding: 3rem 0;
    background: var(--color-bg-darker);
  }

  .container {
    max-width: 1200px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: 0 2rem;
  }

  .pricing-section h2 {
    font-size: 2.5rem;
    color: var(--color-primary);
    text-align: center;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }

  .section-intro {
    text-align: center;
    color: var(--color-text-dim);
    font-size: 1.125rem;
    max-width: 700px;
    margin: 0 auto 4rem;
    line-height: 1.6;
  }

  .pricing-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(300px, 1fr));
    gap: 2rem;
    margin-bottom: 4rem;
    max-width: 900px;
    margin-left: auto;
    margin-right: auto;
  }

  .pricing-card {
    background: rgba(10, 14, 39, 0.8);
    border: 1px solid rgba(0, 212, 255, 0.2);
    border-radius: 16px;
    padding: 2rem;
    position: relative;
    transition: all 0.3s ease;
  }

  .pricing-card:hover {
    transform: translateY(-5px);
    border-color: var(--color-primary);
    box-shadow: 0 20px 40px rgba(0, 212, 255, 0.2);
  }

  .card-supporter  { border-color: rgba(236, 72, 153, 0.35); }
  .card-enterprise { border-color: rgba(0, 212, 255, 0.35); }

  .card-stage {
    display: inline-block;
    font-size: 0.7rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    letter-spacing: 0.1em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    padding: 0.2rem 0.75rem;
    border-radius: 20px;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }

  .stage-supporter  { background: rgba(236,72,153,0.15); color: #EC4899; border: 1px solid rgba(236,72,153,0.35); }
  .stage-enterprise { background: rgba(0,212,255,0.1); color: #00D4FF; border: 1px solid rgba(0,212,255,0.35); }

  .amount-label {
    font-size: 1.5rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: var(--color-text);
  }

  .plan-header {
    text-align: center;
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
    padding-bottom: 2rem;
    border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(224, 224, 224, 0.1);
  }

  .plan-header h3 {
    font-size: 1.5rem;
    color: var(--color-text);
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }

  .price {
    display: flex;
    align-items: baseline;
    justify-content: center;
    gap: 0.25rem;
  }

  .amount {
    font-size: 3rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: var(--color-primary);
  }

  .period {
    font-size: 1rem;
    color: var(--color-text-dim);
  }

  .annual-price {
    font-size: 0.875rem;
    color: var(--color-text-dim);
    margin-top: 0.5rem;
  }

  .features {
    list-style: none;
    padding: 0;
    margin: 0 0 2rem;
  }

  .features li {
    padding: 0.75rem 0;
    color: var(--color-text-dim);
    border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(224, 224, 224, 0.1);
    position: relative;
    padding-left: 1.5rem;
  }

  .features li::before {
    content: "+";
    position: absolute;
    left: 0;
    color: var(--color-primary);
  }

  .btn {
    display: block;
    width: 100%;
    padding: 1rem;
    text-align: center;
    border-radius: 8px;
    font-weight: 600;
    text-decoration: none;
    transition: all 0.3s ease;
  }

  .btn-supporter {
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, #EC4899 0%, #be185d 100%);
    color: white;
  }

  .btn-supporter:hover {
    opacity: 0.9;
    transform: translateY(-2px);
  }

  .btn-enterprise {
    background: transparent;
    color: var(--color-primary);
    border: 2px solid var(--color-primary);
  }

  .btn-enterprise:hover {
    background: var(--color-primary);
    color: var(--color-bg-dark);
  }

  .enterprise-details {
    max-width: 1000px;
    margin: 0 auto 3rem;
  }

  .enterprise-details h3 {
    font-size: 2rem;
    color: var(--color-primary);
    text-align: center;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }

  .enterprise-note {
    text-align: center;
    color: var(--color-text-dim);
    font-style: italic;
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
    font-size: 0.95rem;
  }

  .detail-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(250px, 1fr));
    gap: 2rem;
  }

  .detail-card {
    background: rgba(10, 14, 39, 0.6);
    border: 1px solid rgba(224, 224, 224, 0.1);
    border-radius: 12px;
    padding: 2rem;
    transition: all 0.3s ease;
  }

  .detail-card:hover {
    background: rgba(10, 14, 39, 0.8);
    border-color: rgba(0, 212, 255, 0.2);
  }

  .detail-card h4 {
    color: var(--color-primary);
    font-size: 1.25rem;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }

  .detail-card p {
    color: var(--color-text-dim);
    line-height: 1.6;
  }

  .trust-note {
    max-width: 700px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: 1.5rem 2rem;
    background: rgba(0, 212, 255, 0.04);
    border: 1px solid rgba(0, 212, 255, 0.12);
    border-radius: 10px;
    text-align: center;
  }

  .trust-note h4 {
    font-size: 0.95rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: var(--color-primary);
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.06em;
  }

  .trust-note p {
    font-size: 0.875rem;
    color: rgba(224, 224, 224, 0.55);
    line-height: 1.6;
    margin: 0;
  }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .pricing-grid {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    }
  }
</style>
